			Website powered ⚡️ by our ❤️ for <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" class="text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 underline font-semibold" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Astro's website">Astro</a> & <a href="https://www.solidjs.com/" target="_blank" class="text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 underline font-semibold" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Solid.js website">Solid.js</a>
